<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: Discovery, UX, UI Design</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">Infor Ming.le Chat was a major project that I worked on this year. Our goal was to replace the current Ming.le collaboration platform with a more modern chat platform that would integrate with our ERPs. We designed a seamless chat tool that will allow users to share data, files, and conversation with their teammates while improving their day-to-day workflow.</p>
</section>

