<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">This project required some extensive user research. The current Ming.le collaboration wasn't being adopted by a lot of our users despite being a free feature of the Infor Cloudsuite. We conducted surveys and user interviews to gather information about the current Ming.le and validate our hypothesis that adding a chat feature would make this application more usable.</p>
</section>

<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Solution</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">The data we collected found that most users were paying for other third-party applications like Skype or Slack to communicate with their teams. We knew that by adding these capabilities to Infor's cloudsuite we could convert more users. The finished product was a chat application that include topic-based group coversation and a full team directory for 1-on-1 chats. The development of this appliation is still in process.</p>
</section>

